                "attrs": {
                  "term": "Joconde sponge for Opéra cake",
                  "termId": "cmpde3lb40000egv43qsx698g"
                }
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " sponge soaked in coffee syrup, layered with coffee buttercream and dark chocolate ganache, and finished with a mirror-flat glaze. Make all three components and the coffee syrup before starting assembly. Have everything cold. Chill the cake on a flat tray after each layer goes on."
          }
